TITLE: Implementing a GraphQL Object Type with JavaScript ES6 Class
DESCRIPTION: JavaScript implementation of the RandomDie GraphQL type using an ES6 class with instance methods as resolvers. It includes the root resolver that creates instances of the RandomDie class.
SOURCE: https://github.com/graphql/graphql.github.io/blob/source/src/pages/graphql-js/object-types.mdx#2025-04-08_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
class RandomDie {
  constructor(numSides) {
    this.numSides = numSides
  }

  rollOnce() {
    return 1 + Math.floor(Math.random() * this.numSides)
  }

  roll({ numRolls }) {
    var output = []
    for (var i = 0; i < numRolls; i++) {
      output.push(this.rollOnce())
    }
    return output
  }
}

var root = {
  getDie({ numSides }) {
    return new RandomDie(numSides || 6)
  },
}
```

