TITLE: Generating Static Paths for Tags
DESCRIPTION: Function that generates static paths for all unique tags found in blog posts by extracting tags from frontmatter of pages under the blog route
SOURCE: https://github.com/graphql/graphql.github.io/blob/source/src/pages/tags/[slug].mdx#2025-04-08_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export function getStaticPaths() {
  const items = getPagesUnderRoute("/blog").flatMap(item => item.children || item)
  const tags = items.flatMap(item => item.frontMatter.tags)
  return {
    fallback: false,
    paths: [...new Set(tags)].map(slug => ({ params: { slug } })),
  }
}
```

